"word":"longer","count":1},{"word":"different","count":1},{"word":"gone","count":1},{"word":"bit","count":1},{"word":"recovering","count":1},{"word":"applied","count":1},{"word":"partial","count":1},{"word":"database","count":1},{"word":"mainly","count":1},{"word":"learn","count":1},{"word":"general","count":1},{"word":"knowledge","count":1},{"word":"modern","count":1},{"word":"trends","count":1},{"word":"saw","count":1},{"word":"strolling","count":1},{"word":"around","count":1},{"word":"living","count":1},{"word":"area","count":1},{"word":"facilities","count":1},{"word":"occasionally","count":1},{"word":"lot","count":1},{"word":"new","count":1},{"word":"branches","count":1},{"word":"first","count":1},{"word":"responsible","count":1},{"word":"care","count":1},{"word":"fill","count":1},{"word":"sumika","count":1},{"word":"member","count":1},{"word":"went","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"years","count":1},{"word":"dispatched","count":1},{"word":"team","count":1},{"word":"search","count":1},{"word":"rescue","count":1},{"word":"nothing","count":1},{"word":"solid","count":1},{"word":"came","count":1},{"word":"report","count":1},{"word":"detailed","count":1},{"word":"sumika's","count":1},{"word":"operations","count":1},{"word":"engagements","count":1},{"word":"outstanding","count":1},{"word":"researchers","count":1},{"word":"error","count":1},{"word":"cell","count":1},{"word":"elite","count":1},{"word":"bloom","count":1},{"word":"bearer","count":1},{"word":"made","count":1},{"word":"proud","count":1},{"word":"stellar","count":1},{"word":"matrix","count":1},{"word":"forever","count":1},{"word":"remember","count":1},{"word":"noble","count":1},{"word":"pursuit","count":1},{"word":"truth","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Ah, {PlayerName}. Perfect timing. There's something you need to know.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"Since we took charge of the Honami Sonoro Sphere, we've been noticing some changes on the inside—","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"The link between Honami and the real world is stabilizing, and the city's time flow is almost in sync.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"But scans from Tethys indicate that much of the recent frequency exchanges weren't passing through this rift.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"Meaning it could either just be a misreading due to overlapping data, or... there's another access point to the Honami Sonoro Sphere.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"On top of that, the city's buzzing with unidentified phenomena and unconfirmed hazard zones. We'll continue to monitor them closely and run further analysis.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"She's just completed her treatment. Everything seems to be all right. Her Rabelle's Curve is within normal parameters, and there are no significant lingering Overclocking symptoms.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"That said, I don't recommend repeating what happened in Honami. That level of Resonance strain is unsustainable.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"Ah, excuse me.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"...Yes. Mm-hmm. Got it. {Male=He;Female=She}'s with me right now.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"I just got a call that Chisa submitted an itinerary not long ago and left for Honami alone.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"She didn't specify. All she wrote was \"I want to go back.\"","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"You can find her guide KU-Roro in the Haven of Sprouts. It may know something.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"Anything else you'd like to know? As long as it's within my authority, I can answer.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"After Honami was devastated, energy from the Lament sealed the entire city into a unique Sonoro Sphere like congealed amber. Its time flow was slowed down compared to the rest of the world.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"A similar case would be Mt. Firmament. Being on the inside for a day means up to a hundred days might have passed on the outside.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"But it's not permanent. As Honami's connection to reality grows stronger, the flow of time begins to restore itself.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"You getting sucked into Honami through that rift has got Shorekeeper worried sick, and she's been closely monitoring everything that's going on over there since.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"Good thing is, at that point, Honami's time flow was no longer that different from the real world. So to us, you were only gone for just a bit.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"While she was recovering, Chisa applied for partial access to the Black Shores database, mainly to learn general knowledge and modern trends.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"We also saw her strolling around the living area and taking a look at the facilities occasionally, just like a lot of the New Branches when they first get here.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"The KU-Roro responsible for taking care of her can fill you in if you want to know more.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"Sumika is a member of the Black Shores who went M.I.A. many years ago. We dispatched a team on a search and rescue, but nothing solid came of it.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"The report Chisa submitted to us has detailed Sumika's operations and engagements in Honami.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"She was one of the most outstanding researchers of the Error Cell, and an elite Bloom Bearer who made the Black Shores proud.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004},{"text":"The Stellar Matrix will forever remember her noble pursuit of truth.","quest_name":"Flowing Starlight in the Iris","quest_id":165000004}]}